Description: The Ookaboo RDF dump contains metadata for nearly 1-000-000 public domain and Creative Commons images of more than 500-000 precise topics such as places- people and organism classifications linked to DBpedia and Freebase.Expressed in industry standard RDF- the Ookaboo dump is available with a CC-BY-SA/3.0 license that is friendly for both academic and commercial use. Precision is in excess of 0.98- enabling a new range of applications for image search and classification. See the latest release for downloads and documentation.
